                        "text": "FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#252-345) uses a weak PRNG: \"randomIndex = uint256(keccak256(bytes)(abi.encodePacked(block.timestamp,block.prevrandao,msg.sender,p.balance))) % count (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#313-322)\" \n"
