                        }
                    ],
                    "message": {
                        "text": "Reentrancy in FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#252-345):\n\tExternal calls:\n\t- (success,None) = address(winner).call{value: p.goodValue}() (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#335)\n\tState variables written after the call(s):\n\t- p.status = STATUS_FINISHED (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#340)\n\tFinancialPoolManager.pools (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#68) can be used in cross function reentrancies:\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.activatePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#157-169)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.createPool(string,uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#128-151)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.deletePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#175-184)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#361-388)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.leavePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#216-246)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.participateInPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#190-210)\n"
                    },
                    "ruleId": "slither_0_11_3_reentrancy_eth"
